I'm not sure if it is at full capacity yet. The note from classes.berkeley.edu for the 189 class says:

Initial enrollment capacity is set to 70% of total enrollment until TA hiring is complete. We anticipate total enrollment for the COMBINED class to be 744 seats.

So it's possible that they'll add 100 more to the current 645.  Which still might not help you, given your waitlist number, but increases your odds a little bit.

---------
